387
00:16:41,350 --> 00:16:44,080
Could it all be Vice Censor-in-Chief Du’s doing?

388
00:16:45,620 --> 00:16:48,130
It is him, but not only him.

389
00:16:49,460 --> 00:16:51,320
It would be easier if he was alone.

390
00:16:51,900 --> 00:16:54,170
But I believe there must be

391
00:16:54,510 --> 00:16:56,770
someone behind him pulling the strings.

392
00:16:59,040 --> 00:17:00,920
A hidden mastermind?

393
00:17:02,940 --> 00:17:05,400
There are suspects, but none are confirmed.

394
00:17:06,000 --> 00:17:08,040
The Wen family has been enduring in silence

395
00:17:08,040 --> 00:17:11,150
to catch a bigger fish.

396
00:17:11,520 --> 00:17:14,890
You're just a sickly person who can't hold an official post.

397
00:17:15,250 --> 00:17:17,030
The Wen family never joins factions,

398
00:17:17,030 --> 00:17:18,890
forms cliques, or stirs trouble.

399
00:17:18,960 --> 00:17:20,359
Why would we be targeted?

400
00:17:22,589 --> 00:17:23,119
Yi.

401
00:17:23,839 --> 00:17:25,510
For so many years,

402
00:17:25,560 --> 00:17:28,040
