403
00:17:29,080 --> 00:17:30,320
Do you know why?

404
00:17:30,350 --> 00:17:34,150
To stay away from court politics and disputes.

405
00:17:34,160 --> 00:17:37,170
Yes. The Wen family's status is unique.

406
00:17:37,210 --> 00:17:41,000
Once exposed, it would cause turmoil in the court

407
00:17:41,020 --> 00:17:42,280
and disrupt the peace.

408
00:17:45,380 --> 00:17:47,580
I could only make you endure

409
00:17:47,600 --> 00:17:50,530
the pretense of frailty to ensure

410
00:17:51,190 --> 00:17:53,880
the Wen family's safety for a hundred years.

411
00:17:54,040 --> 00:17:56,730
Remember, never tell outsiders.

412
00:17:57,150 --> 00:18:00,990
