415
00:18:05,650 --> 00:18:08,070
Yes, I'll keep that in mind.

416
00:18:08,730 --> 00:18:11,080
The Wen family oversees the World's Greatest Academy.

417
00:18:11,080 --> 00:18:12,740
Naturally, it attracts envy.

418
00:18:13,280 --> 00:18:14,610
How can we remain aloof?

419
00:18:17,250 --> 00:18:18,250
That makes sense.

420
00:18:20,120 --> 00:18:21,040
Don't worry.

421
00:18:21,070 --> 00:18:22,270
I will protect you...

422
00:18:23,590 --> 00:18:24,770
And the Wen family.

423
00:18:26,890 --> 00:18:30,310
Honey. You've protected your husband very well.

424
00:18:31,000 --> 00:18:32,960
Almost got your husband sold.

425
00:18:34,940 --> 00:18:37,650
Didn't you smile happily just now?

426
00:18:37,670 --> 00:18:39,600
