427
00:18:50,990 --> 00:18:52,100
I was wrong.

428
00:18:52,170 --> 00:18:54,520
I shouldn't have made light of your situation,

429
00:18:54,520 --> 00:18:56,310
nearly causing you to be abducted.

430
00:18:56,310 --> 00:18:58,750
Thankfully, you taught me that word of wisdom.

431
00:18:58,750 --> 00:19:01,310
But now I realize how important learning is.

432
00:19:01,330 --> 00:19:02,100
I promise

433
00:19:02,120 --> 00:19:04,650
I will study hard and make progress every day.

434
00:19:04,650 --> 00:19:05,410
All right.

435
00:19:07,510 --> 00:19:08,330
Get up now.

436
00:19:10,210 --> 00:19:13,160
My previous approach to your studies was too aggressive.

437
00:19:13,160 --> 00:19:15,300
It’s like pulling up seedlings to help them grow faster, which only has the opposite effect.

438
00:19:15,300 --> 00:19:17,260
