00:20:59,970 --> 00:21:00,790
Cheng Manyi!

484
00:21:00,790 --> 00:21:02,000
Thank you.

485
00:21:02,550 --> 00:21:04,310
Cheng Manyi.

486
00:21:04,340 --> 00:21:05,230
Thank you.

487
00:21:18,930 --> 00:21:22,070
What brings you here today, Vice Censor-in-Chief Du?

488
00:21:22,970 --> 00:21:23,920
Mr. Wen!

489
00:21:25,140 --> 00:21:25,990
Mr. Wen.

490
00:21:27,710 --> 00:21:29,910
Your wife slept through class yesterday.

491
00:21:29,910 --> 00:21:32,030
