497
00:21:50,710 --> 00:21:53,830
and fought with the scoundrels.

498
00:21:53,920 --> 00:21:55,490
How inappropriate!

499
00:21:55,520 --> 00:21:57,230
Your wife used my jade chess pieces

500
00:21:57,230 --> 00:21:59,790
as dice during class yesterday.

501
00:22:02,020 --> 00:22:03,900
