504
00:22:08,790 --> 00:22:10,150
How can this be?

505
00:22:10,280 --> 00:22:14,410
Are you talking about Miss Cheng?

506
00:22:14,550 --> 00:22:15,510
Director Du.

507
00:22:15,540 --> 00:22:16,490
That's her.

508
00:22:17,420 --> 00:22:18,330
Strange.

509
00:22:18,840 --> 00:22:21,270
Miss Cheng seems unskilled

510
00:22:21,290 --> 00:22:22,470
and with many faults,

511
00:22:22,470 --> 00:22:25,200
not at all like someone renowned for her talents.

512
00:22:25,790 --> 00:22:26,840
Actually,

513
00:22:27,860 --> 00:22:29,660
I instructed her to act this way.

514
00:22:32,720 --> 00:22:34,180
My wife is quite talented.

515
00:22:34,390 --> 00:22:36,790
I feared that if the students saw her talents,

516
00:22:36,790 --> 00:22:38,520
they might become complacent.

517
00:22:38,550 --> 00:22:41,410
So I had her pretend to be foolish in front of others,

518
00:22:41,510 --> 00:22:44,170
to encourage the students' eagerness to learn.

519
00:22:45,800 --> 00:22:48,890
Hiding one's abilities is not a good strategy.

520
00:22:49,100 --> 00:22:50,730
Revealing them at the right time

521
00:22:50,730 --> 00:22:53,260
can inspire others to study harder.

522
00:22:53,410 --> 00:22:54,480
In my opinion,

523
00:22:54,510 --> 00:22:55,840
tomorrow's qin playing meeting

524
00:22:55,840 --> 00:22:58,280
is a once-in-a-lifetime opportunity.

525
00:22:58,470 --> 00:23:00,830
