531
00:23:15,560 --> 00:23:19,360
Don't worry. I've invited high officials and nobles.

532
00:23:19,390 --> 00:23:21,940
Talented scholars and beautiful ladies will gather

533
00:23:21,940 --> 00:23:25,740
to exchange and discuss. This matter is settled.

534
00:23:26,640 --> 00:23:29,940
May I ask where the qin playing meeting will be held?

535
00:23:30,150 --> 00:23:32,610
Someone will come to inform you tomorrow.

536
00:23:33,220 --> 00:23:34,100
Everyone.

537
00:23:34,650 --> 00:23:37,630
Please come and watch the performance tomorrow.

538
00:23:53,950 --> 00:23:57,260
The combat was unprecedentedly intense.

539
00:23:57,700 --> 00:23:59,890
Unexpectedly, just as things were happening in a flash,

540
00:23:59,890 --> 00:24:03,490
a group of burly men with knives rushed in from the other side.

541
00:24:03,520 --> 00:24:06,310
Luckily, I’ve mastered unparalleled martial arts.

542
00:24:06,310 --> 00:24:09,570
I rushed in and pinned them

543
00:24:09,590 --> 00:24:12,170
to the ground,

544
00:24:12,440 --> 00:24:17,570
leaving them no choice but to beg for mercy.

545
00:24:17,600 --> 00:24:20,320
They had to plead with me to spare them.

546
00:24:25,670 --> 00:24:27,590
I've never heard that you knew martial arts.

547
00:24:27,590 --> 00:24:30,250
Right, aren't you a talented scholar?

548
00:24:30,430 --> 00:24:32,360
Could it be that you were faking it?

549
00:24:36,110 --> 00:24:38,830
I just didn't publicize it before.

550
00:24:38,860 --> 00:24:41,920
I grew up in a martial arts school.

551
00:24:42,270 --> 00:24:46,270
I guess I'm just an ordinary

552
00:24:46,280 --> 00:24:49,860
but well-rounded talent, both in literature and in martial arts.

553
00:24:49,860 --> 00:24:51,180
We can't limit our thinking.

554
00:24:51,180 --> 00:24:52,840
We must broaden our horizons.

555
00:24:54,140 --> 00:24:55,540
Very true.

556
00:24:55,660 --> 00:24:58,710
When one person is far superior to another person,

557
00:24:58,730 --> 00:25:00,720
the latter can only look up in admiration.

558
00:25:00,720 --> 00:25:01,280
You...

559
00:25:02,150 --> 00:25:03,550
Who are you referring to?

560
00:25:05,100 --> 00:25:06,520
After hearing your story,

561
00:25:06,520 --> 00:25:08,440
I am in deep admiration.

562
00:25:08,480 --> 00:25:11,310
May I have your handwriting?

563
00:25:11,340 --> 00:25:13,410
I'll place it in my ancestral home

564
00:25:13,450 --> 00:25:15,510
and burn incense before it every day.

565
00:25:16,000 --> 00:25:18,770
That's not very appropriate.

566
00:25:18,800 --> 00:25:21,220
We should keep a low profile, keep it low-key.

567
00:25:21,220 --> 00:25:22,660
Miss Cheng won't even

568
00:25:22,700 --> 00:25:24,060
do such a small favor?

569
00:25:26,150 --> 00:25:29,400
Manyi, didn’t you say this morning

570
00:25:29,430 --> 00:25:30,800
that you'd gift me the calligraphy

571
00:25:30,800 --> 00:25:32,030
"Serenity Sustains a Thousand Years,

572
00:25:32,030 --> 00:25:33,150
and the Hidden Spring Dwells in Solitude"?

573
00:25:33,150 --> 00:25:34,840
Since our classmate requests it,

574
00:25:34,840 --> 00:25:36,610
why not give it to her first?

575
00:25:39,750 --> 00:25:40,910
Sure, why not?

576
00:25:41,000 --> 00:25:42,160
Sure.

577
00:25:42,330 --> 00:25:44,320
Not at all!

578
00:25:46,120 --> 00:25:48,590
I don't know how to write.

579
00:25:59,900 --> 00:26:00,800
Manyi.

580
00:26:01,160 --> 00:26:03,630
Your hand was injured during the fight yesterday.

581
00:26:03,630 --> 00:26:04,550
I forgot.

582
00:26:04,570 --> 00:26:05,440
Injured?

583
00:26:07,520 --> 00:26:09,700
My hand is injured.

584
00:26:10,340 --> 00:26:11,160
What unfortunate timing.

585
00:26:11,160 --> 00:26:13,390
Then I'll write it on behalf of you today.

586
00:26:13,390 --> 00:26:14,650
Would that be alright?

587
00:26:19,610 --> 00:26:21,520
Could Wei possibly know

588
00:26:21,560 --> 00:26:24,090
that I'm pretending to be a talented scholar?

589
00:26:30,620 --> 00:26:32,410
Well, you...

590
00:26:33,950 --> 00:26:36,030
That outfit looks nice on you.

591
00:26:36,820 --> 00:26:39,820
This is the academy's standard student uniform.

592
00:26:42,500 --> 00:26:43,940
The same as mine.

593
00:26:45,850 --> 00:26:48,010
By the way, your brother...

594
00:26:49,630 --> 00:26:51,630
Has he not finished his studies yet?

595
00:26:52,060 --> 00:26:55,250
My brother doesn't have class today.

596
00:26:55,480 --> 00:26:58,030
No class? Well, I'll be off then.

597
00:26:58,060 --> 00:26:58,750
Manyi.

598
00:27:01,300 --> 00:27:03,170
Are you wondering

599
00:27:03,870 --> 00:27:05,360
if I know

600
00:27:06,070 --> 00:27:08,600
that you're not actually a talented scholar?

601
00:27:09,660 --> 00:27:11,970
What? Manyi is illiterate?

602
00:27:12,540 --> 00:27:15,640
She just doesn't know the Feng State script, that’s all.

603
00:27:15,640 --> 00:27:18,190
This is unbelievable.

604
00:27:19,210 --> 00:27:19,960
Wei.

605
00:27:20,640 --> 00:27:21,830
If you can't accept it...

606
00:27:21,830 --> 00:27:24,630
Manyi is even more extraordinary than I imagined.

607
00:27:25,000 --> 00:27:26,960
Brother, you've truly found a gem.

608
00:27:27,880 --> 00:27:29,210
I'm glad you don't mind.

609
00:27:29,360 --> 00:27:31,990
I have a favor to ask you.

610
00:27:32,590 --> 00:27:34,080
You must protect Manyi,

611
00:27:34,240 --> 00:27:36,230
but also ensure that no one realizes anything is amiss

612
00:27:36,230 --> 00:27:37,760
and takes advantage of her.

613
00:27:51,470 --> 00:27:53,950
You want to play the qin for me?

614
00:27:53,990 --> 00:27:57,110
No, it’s you. You're the one who must play the qin

615
00:27:57,130 --> 00:27:59,130
at tomorrow's qin playing meeting.

616
00:27:59,540 --> 00:28:00,370
What?

617
00:28:00,430 --> 00:28:01,630
I have to play the qin?

618
00:28:01,650 --> 00:28:02,350
Yes.

619
00:28:02,700 --> 00:28:05,020
To ensure that nothing goes wrong, Vice Censor-in-Chief Du

620
00:28:05,020 --> 00:28:06,880
didn't even reveal the location.

621
00:28:12,310 --> 00:28:13,500
This time next year,

622
00:28:13,750 --> 00:28:16,010
you can burn more paper offerings for me.

623
00:28:18,110 --> 00:28:20,230
But not all hope is lost.

624
00:28:23,020 --> 00:28:23,850
Right.

625
00:28:24,470 --> 00:28:25,710
I can't play the qin.

626
00:28:26,230 --> 00:28:27,510
But I can run away.

627
00:28:30,050 --> 00:28:33,410
This is Cheng Manyi, the World's Greatest Talented Woman.

628
00:28:33,630 --> 00:28:36,080
She’s Cheng Manyi?

629
00:28:36,270 --> 00:28:38,770
You are now a walking, living signboard.

630
00:28:39,300 --> 00:28:40,460
Where can you run to?

631
00:28:43,430 --> 00:28:45,780
Could I fake being sick to get out of this?

632
00:28:45,790 --> 00:28:47,320
Delaying won’t work.

633
00:28:47,430 --> 00:28:49,840
Vice Censor-in-Chief Du will simply choose another time.

634
00:28:49,840 --> 00:28:52,530
Young Master, Vice Censor-in-Chief Du has sent word that the qin playing meeting

635
00:28:52,530 --> 00:28:55,660
will be postponed until after the Young Madam recovers.

636
00:29:00,230 --> 00:29:04,330
[Invitation to the Qin Playing Meeting]

637
00:29:01,630 --> 00:29:03,100
The "fake illness" plan

638
00:29:04,430 --> 00:29:05,290
is dead.

639
00:29:27,450 --> 00:29:28,670
You can cover the windows,

640
00:29:28,670 --> 00:29:31,160
but how do you hide from

641
00:29:31,190 --> 00:29:33,320
all the Du's Mansion's many servants?

642
00:29:38,260 --> 00:29:39,390
The "blinding" plan

643
00:29:40,040 --> 00:29:40,880
is dead too.

644
00:29:42,870 --> 00:29:44,320
This won’t work.

645
00:29:44,810 --> 00:29:45,830
That won’t work.

646
00:29:45,860 --> 00:29:47,140
What should I do?

647
00:29:47,170 --> 00:29:47,950
This qin playing meeting

648
00:29:47,950 --> 00:29:50,030
is clearly aimed at me.

649
00:29:50,590 --> 00:29:51,970
I already have a plan.

650
00:29:52,210 --> 00:29:53,500
But for now,

651
00:29:53,750 --> 00:29:54,810
you'll need to learn

652
00:29:54,810 --> 00:29:56,290
to put on a show

653
00:29:56,480 --> 00:29:58,740
and mimic the motions of playing the qin.

654
00:29:59,190 --> 00:30:00,350
What do you mean?

655
00:30:02,580 --> 00:30:04,460
Come, sit.

656
00:30:08,970 --> 00:30:10,830
The qin has

657
00:30:11,480 --> 00:30:15,320
seven strings named Gong, Shang, Jue, Zhi, Yu, Wen, and Wu.

658
00:30:15,740 --> 00:30:18,970
The right hand plucks the strings with techniques

659
00:30:20,780 --> 00:30:28,340
like plucking, sweeping, hooking, flicking, supporting, breaking, striking, and picking.

660
00:30:28,800 --> 00:30:31,860
Your left hand will press the strings to produce tones.

661
00:30:31,860 --> 00:30:33,150
And the right hand

662
00:30:34,950 --> 00:30:35,830
will play the sliding tone.
